he Hello World project is a time-honored tradition in computer programming.
It is a simple exercise that gets you started when learning something new. 
Let’s get started with GitHub!
GitHub is a platform for hosting and collaborating on projects. 
You don’t have to worry about losing data on your hard drive or managing a project across multiple computers — sync from anywhere. 
Most importantly, GitHub is a collaborative and asynchronous workflow for building software better, together.
